rows.label: tlk45700152_02_msg0001
rows.name:
It's not easy to find Silvery Pearl Gems,
even around these parts.

rows.label: tlk45700152_02_msg0002
rows.name:
We get a lot of Ancient Chalices,
but they don't really have much in
the way of technological merit.

rows.label: tlk45700152_02_msg0003
rows.name:
They're more like art pieces, really.
They're these great big pearly-white
vases, good for sticking flowers in.

rows.label: tlk45700152_02_msg0004
rows.name:
The only thing that bugs me about
them is that they have lids attached
for some reason.

rows.label: tlk45700152_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Incidentally, back when Senator
Roderich was younger...

rows.label: tlk45700152_02_msg0006
rows.name:
I heard he filled a whole Ancient
Chalice up with Steam-Gel Ice Cream
and scoffed down the lot!

rows.label: tlk45700152_02_msg0007
rows.name:
Can you imagine?
I'm actually a little jealous...
